data.title: Kraken Robotics Reports Record Q3 2025 Financial Results
data.description: 60% Revenue Growth, 59% Gross Margin, and 25% EBITDA MarginST. JOHN'S, Newfoundland and Labrador, Nov. 24, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Kraken Robotics Inc. (TSX-V: PNG, OTCQB: KRKNF) ("Kraken" or the "Company"), announced it has filed its financial results for the quarter ended September 30, 2025 (“Q3 2025”). Please refer to the unaudited Condensed Consolidated Interim Financial Statements and Management’s Discussion and Analysis (“MD&A”) for quarter ended September 30, 2025, filed on www.sedarplus
